\begin_layout Subsection
Framework: QFT
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let us start with a classical field.
 Consider the simplest case, a real scalar field.
 Imagine a number being assigned to every location in space and time.
 If I demand that the field must satisfy the Klien Gordan equation
