 be shown that 
\begin_inset Formula $[a(\mathbf{p}),a^{\dagger}(\mathbf{p}')]\sim\delta(\mathbf{p}-\mathbf{p}')$
\end_inset

.
 Further, it can be shown that the Hamiltonian for the given Lagrangian,
