 The idea was to factor the Klien Gordan equation.
 So I start with writing an equation of the form 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(i\partial_{\mu}\gamma^{\mu}-m)\psi=0
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset

 are to start with, some parameters (we think of them as numbers to start
 with).
 Now if I multiply this equation with itself (excluding the 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

